        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Veterans Employment Readiness Yield Act of 2025 or the VERY Act of 2025&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill revises terminology used under the Veteran Readiness and Employment program, specifically by replacing the use of &lt;em&gt;employment handicap&lt;/em&gt; with &lt;em&gt;employment barrier&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
